          '\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EApplication Process:&nbsp;Online applications only\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInterested and qualified applicants should apply through ethiojobs website by clicking the green APPLY NOW Button\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E\u003Ca href="https://ethiojobs.net/job/dlGMxAFRvS-audit-manager"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAudit Manager Jobs and Vacancies in Ethiopia | Ethiojobs.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:center;"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EApplication Period:&nbsp;10 days from the date of this notice\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E',
