                        requirement:
                          '\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EQualification and Skills\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EBA or MA&nbsp;in Accounting, and Accounting Finance&nbsp; and related fields.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EExperience:&nbsp;&nbsp;\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMinimum 3&nbsp;\u003C/strong\u003Eyears for MA and 5 years for BA:-\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ERelevant Internal Audit exposures in preaudit and post audit preferably in coffee exporters in PLC, Share companies and others. Knowledge in Tax, Customs and Labor Procamations, Regulations and Directives. Creditors and Debtors accounts reconciliations are strongly required.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESkills:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EAnalytical skills,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003ECommunication skills,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EMS Office skills,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EOrganization and planning skills,\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003ETime management skills\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EReport Writing Skills&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EPeachtree /Accounting/ software Skils\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp style="text-align:justify;"\u003EFinancial data management skills\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E',
