                        requirement:
                          '\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EMinimum of Bachelor Degree in Accounting, Finance, Management, Economics or any related field\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EEight years of experience out of which at least five years on proposal development, budgeting, program and award (grant) management experience\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EExtensive experience in working with key donors including USAID, EC, ECHO, FCDO, NORAD, PRM, BHA &amp; WFP\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EComputer knowledge in MS Office (Excel, Word, etc.)\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAdvanced analytical &amp; MS Excel skill\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EStrong analytical knowledge on budget implications on a long-term basis.&nbsp;\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EFamiliar with Master of budget development/Annual budget planning.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EWillingness and ability to dramatically change work practices, flexible in working long hours and ability to work with incoming surge teams;\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAbility to analyze information, evaluate options and to think and plan strategically.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EPrevious experience&nbsp;of managing and&nbsp; developing&nbsp;a team and the&nbsp; ability to&nbsp;lead, motivate and develop others.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EExcellent interpersonal, communication and presentation skills;\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EVery good in written and spoken English.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EFlexible in event of emergency response;\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ECommitment to Save the Children’s values, vision and mission\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E',
                        how_to_apply:
                          '\u003Cp\u003EPlease attach a copy of your CV and cover letter with your&nbsp;application and&nbsp;include details of your current remuneration and salary expectations.&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUse the below link to&nbsp;apply:&nbsp;&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href="https://hcri.fa.em2.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1"\u003Ehttps://hcri.fa.em2.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWe need to keep children safe so our selection process, which includes rigorous background checks, reflects our commitment to the protection of children from abuse.\u003C/p\u003E',
